{
  "stem": "12506.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I saw that I'm not going to survive this, because it was killing me, seeing  my father in such an agony.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the first time they were looking for builders.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I got up and I said I'm a builder.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they took me away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my father stayed  there in the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I went, at that time-- they took me to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't even have a chance to look back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Once they called your name, they made sure that you run, not walk-- you run.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that's the way life was there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the way I remember it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father, [SIGHS] may he rest in peace, he didn't come home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He must have gone somewhere else, or he maybe could have died in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know where he died, but I know he never came home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's what [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was the destiny, I guess.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We-- we didn't know what's going to happen, but it did happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Today we do know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it's a thing that, today, you talk about civilized people, Germans and all kind of-- they invent everything else, and they invent how to kill people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's something that I could never live with, and I still can't live with it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So at that time, you wouldn't believe it, but it was true.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just plain terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think my biggest agony was seeing my father under those circumstances.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was just terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I couldn't live with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I try to get away from that.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
